<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Viper" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Viper,</orth> the animal Vipera: <cit><quote>I am no v., yet I feed on mother's flesh,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 64</bibl></cit> (cf. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.72" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 72</bibl>). Emblem of mischievous malignancy: <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.129" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 2, 129</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.1.146" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 1, 146</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 3.1.263" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. III, 1, 263</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.285" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 285</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>